room_title: Escape room "Voodoo Cellar" by Eerie Escape in Columbus
room_description:
A house in your neighborhood has been vacant for years, at least as far as you knew. However, one day you notice a mysterious woman peering out through the curtains. Your eyes meet hers and she hurriedly closes the curtains - hoping you didn't see her. Being curious - you wonder - "what is she hiding?"
After seeing the odd woman leave her house, you decide to go take a look. You enter through the cellar door, and once inside, you realize the door has locked behind you. Now you all must find a way out... before she returns!â€‹
